'''Idls Isaggn''' iga yan uḍwar [[Sus|asusi]] itabɛan i taqbilt n [[Isaggn (Ayt Ṣwab)|Isaggn]] [[Ayt Ṣwab]]. Illa uḍwar ad ɣ ammas n idrarn n [[Aṭlas mẓẓiyn|waṭlas mẓẓin]] ɣ tmnaḍt n [[Tamnaḍt n Actukn-Ayt Baha|Actukn-Ayt Baha]] ɣ tsga n [[Tasga n Sus-Massa|Sus-Massa]] ɣ tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]].

Ar ittini usiḍn lli ittyuskar ɣ usggʷas n 2004 mas uḍwar ad zdɣn gis tqriban kran 54 umzdaɣ d 14 n tawjiwin<ref>'''( fr + ar )''' [https://www.webcitation.org/678NyvGs8?url=http://www.lavieeco.com/documents_officiels/Recensement%20population.pdf Asiḍn n n imzdaɣn n Lmɣrib ɣ usggas n 2004] <small>( PDF ) -</small> Tasmirit tamattayt n usɣiws.</ref>.

==Ism==
Idls nɣ Idals, s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|tɛrabt]] ar tt taran s ''إدالس'', s [[Tutlayt Tafransist|tafransist]] ar tt taran s ''Idels''.

'''Idls''' iga yan wawal iḥrfn, tuckad zɣ taguri [[taclḥit]] " ''Adlis''  ", gan as ism ad acku middn lli gis zdɣn tawssan s lḥifḍ nnsn i udlis n rbbi lli igatt [[Lquran]] d tawssan ula s tussna nnsn ɣ kullu mad itɛlqn s ddin [[Lislam]].

